  <part>
    <title>GeneSEZ Core Documentation</title>
    <partintro>
      <para>This section is dedicated to the GeneSEZ core concepts and 
      intentions.</para>
      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term><emphasis role="bold">Goal</emphasis></term>
          <listitem>
            <para>Basic understanding of model driven software 
            development.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
          <term><emphasis role="bold">Prerequisites</emphasis></term>
          <listitem>
            <para>When appropriate we will use UML to visualize 
            relationships or behavior, so a very basic understanding is 
            preferable, but you should be able to grasp the intention 
            anyway.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
    </partintro>
